---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="SIPA校友圈——建设中">

<style>
  .alumni-hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(91,155,213,0.12) 0%, transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(11,44,86,0.15) 0%, transparent 50%),
      #f8f7f4;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* subtle grid texture */
  .alumni-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(11,44,86,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(11,44,86,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 48px 48px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #e5e0d8;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #0B2C56;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(11,44,86,0.07);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .badge .dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #B8860B;
    animation: pulse 2s infinite;
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.5; transform: scale(0.85); }
  }

  .main-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    color: #0B2C56;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .sub {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
  }

  /* feature list */
  .features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: #e5e0d8;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 720px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(11,44,86,0.07);
    position: relative;
  }
  .feature {
    background: #fff;
    padding: 1.6rem 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
    display: block;
  }
  .feature-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #0B2C56;
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }
  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: #888;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* timeline hint */
  .timeline-hint {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: #aaa;
    max-width: 400px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .timeline-hint strong {
    color: #555;
  }

  /* back link */
  .back-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #5B9BD5;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: color .2s;
  }
  .back-link:hover { color: #0B2C56; }
</style>

<section class="alumni-hero">
  <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center w-full">

    <div class="badge">
      <span class="dot"></span>
      即将上线 · Coming Soon
    </div>

    <h1 class="main-title">
      SIPA 校友圈
    </h1>

    <p class="sub">
      一个专属于 SIPA 学生与校友的社区——在这里找到同频的人，共同面对求职、职场和人生的岔路口。
    </p>

    <!-- Feature cards -->
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">🌆</span>
        <div class="feature-title">城市聚会 & 活动</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">纽约、北京、上海、香港……在你所在的城市找到 SIPA 的朋友</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">🤝</span>
        <div class="feature-title">职场内推</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">金融、咨询、政策、科技——校友互帮互助，让第一份工作更顺利</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">💬</span>
        <div class="feature-title">经验交流</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">申请攻略、选课心得、求职复盘——少走弯路，多走直路</div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <span class="feature-icon">🌐</span>
        <div class="feature-title">全球校友网络</div>
        <div class="feature-desc">连接分布在世界各地的 SIPA 人，把校友资源真正用起来</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="timeline-hint">
      这个板块还在搭建中。如果你是 SIPA 在读生或校友，<br/>
      <strong>欢迎联系我，一起把这个社区做起来。</strong>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a href="/join/"
         class="no-underline px-7 py-3 bg-columbia-navy text-white font-semibold text-sm rounded-full
                hover:bg-[#0d3568] transition-all shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5 active:translate-y-0">
        联系我，参与建设 →
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="back-link">
        ← 返回首页
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

</Base>
